Hello,
> May be I am missing something here.  Are we discussing the PCI config
> status after PCI probing is completed?  Or are we at the entry point for
> the device sub-systems?
   You can freely access the PCI configuration registers except for region
base registers and the interrupt line register, because the exact meaning
of these registers is architecture dependent and connected with the
resource management stuff as well.
